      • getLookupMatchingField

        public java.lang.String getLookupMatchingField()
        This method will look up the value of "matchingField" it will then return the value of the variable name which matches it. NOTE: This method requires that the result has been elaborated, or else data is potentially missing. As an alternate you can use "getMatchingFieldValue" to use the data returned from search server.
        Returns:
        String of the matching field value
